    <thetext>Description of problem:
Swig doesn&apos;t seem to support php7 which is causing several build failures. E.g. graphviz. I had to disable the php bindings till resolved.

Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable):
swig-3.0.10-1.fc25

How reproducible:
Always

Steps to Reproduce:
1. try to rebuild graphviz with enabled php

Actual results:
Fails on various zend* syntax errors.

Expected results:
No errors.

Additional info:
Swig upstream is aware of the problem:
https://github.com/swig/swig/issues/571</thetext>
